The two main components of this total are:
1. "Total Current Liabilities"
   - Initial value: 0.00 (on 2023-12-31)
   - End value: 2491297.55 (on 2024-01-30)

2. "Total Owner's Equity"
   - Initial value: 13000000.00 (on 2023-12-31)
   - End value: 11598563.11 (on 2024-01-30)

Let me format this into the required JSON structure:

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '13000000.00', 'end value': '14089860.66', 'sub_items': {'initial sub_item value1': '0.00', 'end sub_item value1': '2491297.55', 'initial sub_item value2': '13000000.00', 'end sub_item value2': '11598563.11'}}}
```
